Eksteen earlier denied showing alleged middleman Luthando Siyoni photographs of Jayde s body during the questioning of him at the Organised Crime offices on April 28 last year.But in a recording of Eksteen speaking to Christopher s father Costa Panayiotou he tells him how they instructed Siyoni to look at the graphic pictures.Eksteen meanwhile also told the court that at some stage Costa his friend of 16 years told him he wanted to write his son off because of his affair with Chanelle Coutts. Costa was angry he didn t even go to the OK Grocer because of it. Eksteen returns to the stand on Tuesday afternoon.